3 thank you car !	you are welcome my driver !

3 for the whole week , please !	the weather next 7 days for compton is going to be a series of ups and downs from foggy on sunday to a foggy on thursday and to dry on friday the highs are forecast to be near 100f with lows near 20f
4 thank you so much for the information	you are welcome have a good day

3 for the whole week , please !	the weather next 7 days for manhattan is going to be a series of ups and downs from foggy on wednesday to a clear_skies on thursday and to snow on friday the highs are forecast to be near 100f with lows near 20f
4 thank you so much for the information	you are welcome have a good day
